title: 2010.09.11-F1.14.Italy.Qualifying.BBC1_UK [TDMK1]
description:
2010.09.11-F1.14.Italy.Qualifying.BBC1_UK-TDMK1.m4v

Jake Humphrey is at the Autodromo Nazionale Monza to present the qualifying session for the 14th race of the season (Start-time 1.00pm). Lewis Hamilton claimed pole position here last year, but failed to earn any points in the race, crashing out on the final lap while in third place. Commentary by Jonathan Legard and Martin Brundle.

Now encoded as 'MP4 All Play'... As a departure from the DivX files which I have uploaded in the past, I've made the decision to get with the 21st century & start encoding with the following specs this year;

MP4 - 640x352 - 800Kb/s H264 Video - 44.1KHz/128Kbps Stereo AAC Audio

My belief is this is the best all round setup, and hopefully you will agree!

This video will play on a computer with VLC, XBMC, XBox360, PS3, iPad all iPhones - enjoy the show... :)
